title.narrative: Fostering Innovation through Research, Science and Technology (FIRST)

description.narrative: The project development objective is to support science, technology and innovation (STI) in Vietnam by designing and piloting of STI policies, enhancing the effectiveness of project-aided research and development (R&D) institutions, and encouraging the development of innovative technology enterprises.
